pageProduct.description:

General Information

Gluten Free, Low Carb, high protein mini protein bar

Warnings

Contains milk, peanuts, soy, and sesame seeds.

Ingredients

Protein Blend 31% (Soy Protein Isolate, Whey Protein Isolate, Whey Protein Concentrate, Soy Protein Nuggets, Calcium Caseinate), No Added Sugar Protein Milk Chocolate 18% (Maltitol, Cocoa Solids 33%, Milk Solids 20%, Soy Protein Isolate, Emulsifiers (Soy Lecithin, 476), Natural Vanilla Flavour), Polydextrose, Maltitol, Sorbitol, Caramel Paste 8% (Invert Sugar, Humectants (Sorbitol, Glycerol), Concentrated Pear Puree, Polydextrose, Sunflower Oil, Citrus Fibre, Natural Colours (Caramel I, Titanium Dioxide), Gelling Agent (Pectin), Firming Agent (Calcium Lactate), Natural Flavour), Humectant (Glycerol), Peanuts 4.5%, Sunflower Oil, Sugar Free Caramel Chips 1%, Flavour, Natural Colour (Caramel I), Emulsifier (Soy Lecithin), Salt, Sweetener (Steviol Glycosides), Antioxidant (Vitamin E). Milk protein chocolate contains 20% milk solids minimum.
